title: Week 5 Rankings 2022
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp talk injuries, what players can stay hot & what players can finally break out including if Josh Jacobs and Dameon Pierce are here to stay. Plus, Liz Loza joins to tell us if Terry McLaurin breaks out this week and answer your social questions.
